[{"id":"VH917156","type":"mcq","stimulusHtml":"<div>\n<div class=\"stimulus_reference\">\n<div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure presents a horizontal segment of wire in a uniform magnetic field between the opposite poles of two magnets, and a force diagram. The segment of wire has current I moving horizontally toward the reader. The magnetic field has magnitude B, and is horizontal and perpendicular to the wire, moving to the right. The force diagram shows a force toward the top of the page labeled “F sub B” and a force toward the bottom of the page labeled “W sub wire.” F sub B is significantly longer than W sub wire.\" height=\"161\" src=\"https://assets.learnosity.com/organisations/537/VH917156.g01.png\" width=\"400\" /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"stem_paragraph\">A uniform horizontal segment of wire with length <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"l\"><math alttext=\"l\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mo>ℓ</mo></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> and mass <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"m\"><math alttext=\"m\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mi>m</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> carries a current <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"I\"><math alttext=\"I\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mi>I</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> . It is placed in a uniform magnetic field of magnitude <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"B\"><math alttext=\"B\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mi>B</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> that is horizontal and perpendicular to the wire, as shown above. A student draws the force diagram shown. What is the acceleration of the wire?</p>\n","rubricRef":"VH917156_rubric","choicesHtml":["<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"I l B\"><math alttext=\"I l B\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mi>I</mi><mo>ℓ</mo><mi>B</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"the fraction I l B over m\"><math alttext=\"the fraction I l B over m\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mi>I</mi><mo>ℓ</mo><mi>B</mi><mo>/</mo><mi>m</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"I l b  minus m g\"><math alttext=\"I l b  minus m g\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mi>I</mi><mo>ℓ</mo><mi>B</mi><mrow><mo>−</mo><mi>m</mi><mi>g</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"open parenthesis, the fraction I l B over m, close parenthesis, minus g\"><math alttext=\"open parenthesis, the fraction I l B over m, close parenthesis, minus g\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi>I</mi><mo>ℓ</mo><mi>B</mi><mo>/</mo><mi>m</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>−</mo><mi>g</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span></p>"],"answer":3}]